            "type": "text",
            "text": "Kokoro streaming audio provides a robust solution for real-time audio processing, enabling low-latency streams ideal for applications like live transcription and interactive voice systems. This guide offers practical, non-fluffy guidance for API teams to integrate and optimize Kokoro streaming audio in production environments."
          }
        ]
