            "type": "text",
            "text": "1. API Authentication and Client Setup"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Begin by obtaining API credentials from the Kokoro dashboard. Use standard OAuth 2.0 or API key authentication for secure access. Install the official Kokoro SDK for your programming language (e.g., Python, Node.js) via package managers. Initialize the client with your credentials and set the base URL to the Kokoro streaming endpoint. Ensure error handling is implemented for authentication failures, such as retrying with exponential backoff."
          }
        ]
      },
